  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/internet/\" rel=\"tag\">互联网络</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/23/pope-francis-sees-the-internet-as-a-blessing-for-communication/\"><img alt=\"Pope Francis on Twitter\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/f875fae152e3e0e4777408ff3699eb3/pope-francis-on-twitter.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n对有些人来说，网络会致使其<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/09/16/study-finds-that-anger-spreads-further-on-social-networks/\">愤怒</a>或<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2010/08/03/study-claims-internet-addicted-teens-more-likely-to-suffer-depre/\">上瘾</a>，但在教皇 Francis 眼中，显然看到了更为积极的一面。在为天主教会世界传播日准备的<a href=\"http://www.news.va/en/news/communication-at-the-service-of-an-authentic-cultu\">致辞</a>中，他称互联网是「上帝的礼物」，能帮助人们更好地交流，体会不同的想法，唤起大家团结的意识。当然，教宗也深知滥用网络的弊端。网民可能会选择性地看待只符合自己想法的事物，而且过度依赖网络可能会让人与人之间面对面的机会变得更少。但不管怎么说，他还是认为网际网络中「满含着人性」和善良，只要我们付出努力，这个地方就会变得更加美好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/01/23/pope-francis-sees-the-internet-as-a-blessing-for-communication/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2014/1/23/5337508/pope-francis-says-the-internet-is-a-gift-from-god\" target=\"_blank\">The Verge</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.news.va/en/news/communication-at-the-service-of-an-authentic-cultu\" target=\"_blank\">News.va</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/23/pope-francis-sees-the-internet-as-a-blessing-for-communication/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20814434/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/23/pope-francis-sees-the-internet-as-a-blessing-for-communication/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
  "title": "教皇 Francis：互联网是交流的福音"
